    "description": "<p>You can spend<strong> 1 AP </strong>and <strong>1 MP</strong> to imbue 1 Weapon that you are holding with divine energy for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>For the duration, the Weapon emits Bright Light (you choose the light&rsquo;s appearance) in a 5 Space radius and you gain a bonus equal to your <strong>Prime Modifier </strong>on <strong>Attack Checks </strong>you make with the Weapon.</p>\n<p>The effect ends early if you cease holding or carrying the Weapon, you fall Unconscious, or you choose to end it for free.</p>",
